quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  24,32,"Resinee …ďe resaali …ďen e moo…óon e mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďen immorde e muccu…ďe moo…óon e hor…ďe moo…óon, si …ďe laatike waasu…ďe Alla al…óinay …ďe immorde e ∆Āural Makko ngal, Alla ko O Yaaju…óo Anndu…óo"
  24,33,"∆Āe he…ďaali feere resugol …ďen yo …ďe habbo haa Alla al…óinira …ďe ∆Āural Makko ngal. ∆Āen wonu…ďe …óa…ď…ďude soottaade e …ďen …ďe √Īaame moo…óon jeyi, soottaadede …ďe si on anndii e ma…ď…ďe mo∆ī∆īere, jonnee …ďe immorde e jawdi Alla ndin, ndin ndi O jonni on, wata on waawnu hor…ďe moo…óon …ďen e fii jeeno, si …ďe faandike saŇčaade, wata on …óa…ď…ďu jawkal ngurndam aduna, kala waawnuu…óo …ďe pellet, Alla …ďaawo baawnugol …ďe ko O Surroowo Yurmitee…óo"
  24,34,"Gom…óii Men jippinii e moo…óon Aayeeje …ďanngu…óe e misal immorde e …ďeya wulinoo…ďe ko adii on e waaju wonannde huloo…ďe [Alla] …ďen"
  24,35,"Ko Alla woni Ndaygu kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, sifa Ndaygu Makko ngun ko wano tu…ó…óere hara no e mayre pitilol(lampu), pitilol ngol wona e nder biiniiri, biiniiri ndin hara hindi wa'i wa hoodere jalbunde hinde hu…ď…ďa immorde e leggal barkinaangal nebbantewal ngal wonaa funnaangeyankowal ngal wonaa hirnaangeyankowal nebban maggal …óan no …ďadoo jalbude, hay si yiite meemaali …óan, ndaygu e hoore ndaygu, Alla no fewnira ndaygu Makko ngun on mo O Muuyi, Alla no piyana yim…ďe …ďen mise, Alla ko O Anndu…óo kala huunde. @Corrected"
  24,36,E nder cuu…ói …ói Alla duŇčii(sakkiti) yo darne Innde Makko jantee e nder majji Subunhinanee Mo nder majji ka bimmbi e ka kiikii…óe
